Server.js - is where we register Express, its the entry point

install node.js 

npm init -y : creates the package.json

npm i express 

npm i -g nodemon : automatically and detects when theres a change

.env helps to keep your code hidden from outside sources 

npm i dotenv : loads env variable into the process object in a node.js environment 

npm i bcrypt 
 
npm i jsonwebtoken

